headline: Quanta Services Announces Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: Quanta Services, Inc. (NYSE: PWR) announced today that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly cash dividend to stockholders of $0.10 per share, or a rate of $0.40 per share on an annualized basis. The dividend is payable on July 11, 2025, to stockholders of record as of July 1, 2025.
